enhanced_by.reason: The startNode_ method must be called before createNode_ to initialize the table structure.
The createChildrenVector method should be called to create the children vector before passing its offset to createNode_.
The createEntriesVector method should be called to create the entries vector before passing its offset to createNode_.
The endNode_ method is called at the end of createNode_ to finalize the table structure and return the offset.
The getRootAsNode_ method can be used to verify the correctness of the created node by comparing it with the expected structure.
